General.Name: Edri-El
General.Description: Edri-El Israel Assets Ltd. initiates, develops, constructs, leases, manages, and maintains commercial investment properties in Israel. It serves tenants of commercial areas/offices in various industries, including fashion, food, electricity, electronics, finance, health, and transportation industries. The company was formerly known as Edri-El Holdings Ltd. Edri-El Israel Assets Ltd. was founded in 2006 and is based in Tel Aviv, Israel.
